---
title: Moroccan Beef Tagine with Charred Zucchini, Couscous and Flaked Almonds
description: The word ragout comes from the French word meaning ‘to revive the flavour’. So, jump right in and have yourself a flavour revival with our Middle Eastern twist on beef ragout!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moroccan-beef-tagine-6f837530.jpg
